\c 114
\s Simba raJehovha parwendo rwaVaIsraeri
\p
\v 1 Pakubuda kwaIsraeri Imba yaJakove ichibuda pakati pavanhu vakange vanorumwe rurimi.
\v 2 Judha akaitwa imba yake tsvene, naIsraeri ushe hwake.
\p
\v 3 Gungwa rakazviona, rikatiza; Joridhani rwakadzokera shure.
\v 4 Makomo akapembera samakondobwe, nezvikomo samakwayana.
\p
\v 5 Unonzweiko iwe gungwa, zvaunotiza iwe? Newe Joridhani, zvaunodzokera shure?
\v 6 Nemwi makomo, zvamunopembera samakondobwe; nemwi zvikomo, samakwayana?
\p
\v 7 Bvunda iwe pasi, pamberi paShe, pamberi paMwari waJakove.
\v 8 Iye akashandura dombo, rikava dziva remvura, (add missing).
